        <header class="mb-8">
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
            <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-blue-600">← Back to Blog</a>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Advanced Video Surveillance Technology: How S-VIDIA Powers Modern Security</h1>
